  <div class="nhsuk-grid-row">
    <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-two-thirds">



										
        
          <p>All content must meet at least level AA of the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG 2.0). Aim for AAA where possible.</p>

          <p>To understand how to achieve this, use:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>our <a href="/practices/make-your-service-accessible">guide to making your NHS service accessible</li>
              <li>the <a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/tips/writing/">Web Accessibility Initiative (WAI) guide to writing for web accessibility</a></li>
            </ul>
          <p>As well as writing content that is accessible, we make sure that no one feels that our language excludes them. Read more about <a href="/content/inclusive-language">inclusive language</a> in the digital service manual.</p>



    </div>


